dc_title_s: Tripoli 1:100,000. Gasr Iefren. Sheet 1573. Series Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. Provisional G.S.G.S. 3980. United States. Army Map Service. Alternate title: 1:100,000 Tripoli. Sheet 1573, Gasr Iefren. Relief shown by 25 metres and 5 metre (approximate) contour interval and spot heights. Reproduced by Great Britain. Army. Royal Engineers. Field Survey Coy., 512 (A. Fd. Svy) Coy R. E. from Italian 1:100,000 sheet, Gasr Iefren, published by the Istituto Geografico Militare, 1934. Revised by 512 Fd. Svy. Coy, R.E. Dec., 1942. Map is part of a set of 31 sheets.
